<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Pizzaria Bella Massa</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
    background:#fff8f0;
}

header{
    background:#c62828;
    position:fixed;
    width:100%;
    top:0;
    z-index:1000;
}

nav{
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:auto;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    padding:15px 20px;
}

.logo{
    color:#fff;
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

nav ul{
    list-style:none;
    display:flex;
    gap:20px;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.hero{
    height:100vh;
    background:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513104890138-7c749659a591?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=80');
    background-size:cover;
    background-position:center;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
}

.overlay{
    background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    padding:40px;
    border-radius:15px;
}

.hero h1{
    color:white;
    font-size:4rem;
}

.hero p{
    color:white;
    font-size:1.2rem;
    margin:15px 0;
}

.btn{
    background:#ff6f00;
    color:white;
    border:none;
    padding:15px 30px;
    border-radius:8px;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-size:18px;
    transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#e65100;
}

section{
    padding:80px 20px;
}

.titulo{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:2.5rem;
    color:#c62828;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

.cardapio{
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:30px;
}

.card{
    width:320px;
    background:white;
    border-radius:15px;
    overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    transition:.3s;
}

.card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-10px);
}

.card img{
    width:100%;
    height:220px;
    object-fit:cover;
}

.card h3{
    padding:15px;
}

.card p{
    padding:0 15px;
}

.preco{
    display:block;
    padding:15px;
    color:#c62828;
    font-size:24px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.sobre{
    text-align:center;
    max-width:800px;
    margin:auto;
    font-size:1.1rem;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.contato{
    text-align:center;
    background:#c62828;
    color:white;
}

footer{
    background:#222;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

    nav{
        flex-direction:column;
        gap:10px;
    }

    nav ul{
        flex-wrap:wrap;
        justify-content:center;
    }

    .hero h1{
        font-size:2.5rem;
    }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <nav>
        <div class="logo">🍕 Bella Massa</div>

        <ul>
            <li><a href="#inicio">Início</a></li>
            <li><a href="#cardapio">Cardápio</a></li>
            <li><a href="#sobre">Sobre</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contato">Contato</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero" id="inicio">
    <div class="overlay">
        <h1>A Melhor Pizza da Cidade</h1>
        <p>Massa artesanal, ingredientes frescos e muito sabor.</p>
        <button class="btn" onclick="pedido()">Peça Agora</button>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="cardapio">
    <h2 class="titulo">Nosso Cardápio</h2>

    <div class="cardapio">

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513104890138-7c749659a591?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80">
            <h3>Pizza Margherita</h3>
            <p>Molho de tomate, mussarela e manjericão fresco.</p>
            <span class="preco">R$ 39,90</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565299624946-b28f40a0ae38?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80">
            <h3>Pizza Calabresa</h3>
            <p>Calabresa especial, cebola e queijo premium.</p>
            <span class="preco">R$ 44,90</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571407970349-bc81e7e96d47?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80">
            <h3>Pizza Portuguesa</h3>
            <p>Presunto, ovos, cebola, ervilha e azeitonas.</p>
            <span class="preco">R$ 49,90</span>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section id="sobre">
    <h2 class="titulo">Sobre Nós</h2>

    <div class="sobre">
        Há mais de 20 anos, a Bella Massa oferece pizzas artesanais
        preparadas com ingredientes selecionados, forno especial e
        receitas tradicionais italianas. Nosso objetivo é entregar
        sabor, qualidade e uma experiência inesquecível.
    </div>
</section>

<section class="contato" id="contato">
    <h2 class="titulo" style="color:white;">Contato</h2>

    <p>📞 (11) 99999-9999</p>
    <br>
    <p>📍 Rua das Pizzas, 123 - Centro</p>
    <br>
    <button class="btn" onclick="pedido()">Fazer Pedido</button>
</section>

<footer>
    © 2026 Bella Massa - Todos os direitos reservados.
</footer>

<script>
function pedido(){
    alert("🍕 Pedido iniciado! Entraremos em contato em breve.");
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
